Package: au.com.redboxresearchdata.harvester.csvjdbc

[Groovy] Class CsvJdbcBridge

    • au.com.redboxresearchdata.harvester.csvjdbc.CsvJdbcBridge
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      org.relique.io.TableReader, org.springframework.scheduling.Trigger, org.springframework.integration.context.OrderlyShutdownCapable

      class CsvJdbcBridge

      Bridges Spring Integration's file and JDBC mechanisms for CSVJDBC's file-specific awareness. The assumption is that the instance is used in linear fashion, as in a chain.

      Authors:
      Shilo Banihit
      Since:
      1.0
